czmq (3.0.2-4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add 0004-zauth-v2-test-hang.patch to fix test.
    Backport patch from upstream to fix unit test race
    condition in zauth_v2.
  * Don't fail build if UT fail on slower archs.
    There are known upstream issues with race conditions
    in the unit tests, that can cause a failure on slower
    environments. As a workaround, have a failure in
    dh_auto_test stop the build only on amd64 and i386.

 -- Luca Boccassi <luca.boccassi@gmail.com>  Wed, 09 Mar 2016 16:53:58 +0000

